HEADWORD: Urtication
<hw>Ur`ti*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>The act or process of whipping or stinging with nettles; --
sometimes used in the treatment of paralysis.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

